'When you're growing up you're asked, "If
you could have one wish, what would you wish for?" Back in those days, I
used to say, "As many wishes as I could wish for." Now, my only wish 
would be for my dog to come home,' Mr Simpson said.

Since Mr Cutie went missing friends have put posters up searching for him around Mr Simpson's home.

But so far, no one has found the dog and, since he has been lost, the area has been hit by Tropical Storm Andrea.

