As word of the Mr Simpson's dying wish spread however, a Facebook campaign by Life With Dogs has attracted more than 2,000 likes and shares as dog lovers join the search to find Mr Cutie.

'This is part of a project, the last thing on earth to do is to get my dog back,' Mr Simpson said.

'Part of me feels like I can go in peace if that happens.

